    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next chapter? I\u2019m selling my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic companion. It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-loved, running smoothly and ready to hit the road whenever you are! It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being broken-in and dependable, making it a great choice for daily commutes or fun weekend trips. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love driving it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
