    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the rev range. This unit is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and utilizes the factory variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring precise lateral stability and communicative steering feedback. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains mechanically robust and ready for spirited use.",
