    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver that has been treated with care. The exterior finish retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you may find the occasional minor stone chip or light surface scratch typical of respectful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and entirely smoke-free; the leather upholstery remains supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every electronic component, from the premium audio system to the dual-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has a comprehensive service history, including a recent professional inspection, oil change, and brake service. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and service records. This is a solid, honest car that is ready to be driven home today without any immediate maintenance concerns.",
