      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle exhibits a commendable balance of performance and long-term reliability. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, it retains a high degree of mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. The interior remains refined, reflecting a history of careful stewardship. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a sophisticated vehicle that delivers both prestige and dependable service.",
      "price": 36500.0,
