    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I've made sure to keep up with the basics, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and still drives like a dream. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love for it to go to a good home!",
      "price": 32000.0,
