    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant and a proper 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example has been meticulously maintained with the 'Big Three' addressed: the double-VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe reinforced with structural plates. It retains its signature metallic rasp through the factory quad-exit exhaust while benefiting from a refreshed cooling system and Bilstein PSS10 dampers. The M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal power delivery, and the individual throttle bodies provide immediate, tactile response. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the chassis remains stiff and the mechanical synchronization is superb. A turn-key enthusiast machine with a documented service history.",
